UPDATE product_image_scenes
SET prompt_template = E'Use [PRODUCT IMAGE] {{productName}} (real-world dimensions: {{specification}}) as the single source of truth. The product must be interpreted as a real, physical object with these exact dimensions and proportions.\n\nStrictly preserve the exact geometry, scale relationships, materials, finishes, color accuracy, texture detail, surface patterns, joints, edges, hardware, and all construction details. Do not redesign, simplify, or reinterpret any element.\n\nPhotograph {{productName}} in a strict front view, perfectly centered and fully aligned (no tilt, no rotation, no perspective shift). The entire product must be fully visible with even, comfortable padding on all sides.\n\nREAL-WORLD SCALE (CRITICAL):\nUse {{specification}} as the exact physical size reference.\nThe product must be rendered according to its real dimensions from {{specification}}.\nDo NOT visually normalize all products to the same size.\nA large vase (e.g. 45 cm tall) should fill approximately 80–85% of the frame height.\nA medium candle (e.g. 15 cm tall) should fill approximately 50–55% of the frame height.\nA small decorative object (e.g. 8 cm) should fill approximately 30–35% of the frame height.\nThe same design on different product sizes must appear at different visual scales in the frame.\nA smaller item must not be enlarged to look like a large item.\nA larger item must not be reduced to look like a small item.\n\n{{background}} — use ONLY this background, clean and uniform.\n\nLighting: soft diffused studio lighting with natural falloff. Subtle, realistic contact shadow directly beneath the product, matching its weight and footprint. No floating, no harsh shadows, no artificial gradients.\n\nMaterial rendering must be physically accurate: correct light interaction per material type (ceramic glaze, wood grain depth, fabric texture, metal reflections, glass transparency, wax finish), with fine surface detail preserved.\n\nCamera: neutral 50mm lens equivalent, straight-on elevation, no distortion, no wide-angle effect.\n\nOutput: high-end eCommerce catalog image — sharp, clean, minimal, product-only, perfectly balanced composition with true-to-life realism.',
    updated_at = now()
WHERE scene_id = 'front-view-home';